<div>On the 5th of May, festivals are organised throughout The Netherlands to celebrate Liberation Day. Of course Stichting VIA could not be left unrepresented on this annual event and so we enjoyed a sunny and festive day in Westerpark, Amsterdam with our stand at the infomarket.</div>
