			<title>Elin in Jordan</title>
			<link>http://www.via.dds.nl/joomla2/index.php/nieuws-140/258-elin-jordan</link>
			<guid isPermaLink="true">http://www.via.dds.nl/joomla2/index.php/nieuws-140/258-elin-jordan</guid>
			<description><![CDATA[<div class="feed-description"><p><img src="http://www.via.dds.nl/joomla2/via-media/content/nieuws/algemeen/elin/elin-jordan.jpg" border="0" alt="" /></p>
<p>Elin, a VIA volunteer who was the coordinator of the Asylum seeker centrum project that VIA did in Almelo during the summer is heading for a new experience. She will participate in a long term volunteering project in Jordan organized by SCI, where she will be volunteering in a refugee camp with Syrian refugees.</p>
