			<title>You too can volunteer</title>
			<link>http://www.via.dds.nl/joomla2/index.php/nieuws-140/240-you-too-can-volunteer</link>
			<guid isPermaLink="true">http://www.via.dds.nl/joomla2/index.php/nieuws-140/240-you-too-can-volunteer</guid>
			<description><![CDATA[<div class="feed-description"><p><img style="margin: 2px; float: left;" alt="you too can volunteer" src="http://www.via.dds.nl/joomla2/via-media/content/nieuws/algemeen/nieuws/you too can volunteer.jpg" height="127" width="238" />The preparation team (of which I am proud to be a part) is working hard to make it as exciting as possible. It shouldn't be difficult with amazing speakers that will appear and share fascinating SCI stories. The live SCI talk show 'You TOO Can Volunteer' will take place on Sunday, March 24<sup>th</sup> ,1 pm sharp!</p>
<p>Service Civil International is one of the world's largest international volunteering organisations of which VIA is the Dutch branch. During the live show we will be hosting speakers from all over the world talking about various projects that you can join.</p>
